{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63df2b5c32","title":"对一封反映广东潮汕地区整风情况的来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ace842a0e","index":0,"year":1958,"month":4,"day":27,"articleId":"63df2b5c32"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"abdc8dba7a","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陶铸，当时任中共广东省委第一书记。"},{"id":"d31d448715","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"广东省潮安县有人于1958年4月1日给中共中央办公厅写信，反映潮安县委书记在整风反右斗争中自杀的情况。来信希望从速派人到潮汕检查该地区整风中的反地方主义运动，及时解决存在的问题，使整风运动健康发展。"}],"contents":[{"id":"da7b2b9b09","type":"title","text":"对一封反映广东潮汕地区整风情况的来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32"},{"id":"abdc8dba7a","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32"},{"id":"d31d448715","type":"paragraph","text":"此件所提问题，请派一个政治上强的同志去彻查一次。宗派主义可能有的，但死者有无因而致死的特殊情况，也值妥善详查。去的人不要带任何预定估计，完全从寻找真理出发。情况弄清，群疑可释。闻你病了，要静心养病，好了再工作，不急忙。潮汕这件事件，可用几句话交付一位书记去办就行了","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32"},{"id":"57ec639ca0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32"},{"id":"544703b9fe","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32"}],"page":{"id":"a696b6da0a","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"63df2b5c32","start":257,"end":257}}}},"__N_SSG":true}